dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Text on verso with title: Description de Brasil. Probably issued in: Le theatre du monde, ou, Nouvel atlas .... / mis en lumiere par Guillaume & Iean Blaeu. A Amsterdam : Iean Blaeu, 1647.
